	  compiler warnings (and more requested)

2006-06-24 00:11  strk

	* lwgeom/lwpostgis.sql.in: Added spaces between parameters ref and
	  operator, as pgsql 7.3 chokes otherwise ($1*$2 becomes $1 * $2)

