2002-12-05 22:12  pramsey

	* postgis.sql.in: Returned to 'opaque' as type in creation, since
	  7.3 will automatically
	  cast and < 7.3 will fail if I use a different value. This causes
	  some
	  warnings in 7.3, but no failures.

